high_descs: Turn around and walk to the door on your right, then turn to your left and walk across the kitchen, to the sink.
Pick up the egg to the left of the faucet, on the back of the counter.
Move over to your left slightly, so that you are in front of the top cabinets, to the left of the sink.
Place the egg on a plate that is on the bottom shelf inside the cabinet.
Remove the plate, with the egg on it, from the cabinet.
Turn to your right and go to the counter just past the sink, on your right.
Place the plate, with the egg on it, near the edge of the counter to the the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate containing an egg on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and take one step then turn left and walk across the room.
Pick up the egg from the counter.
Turn left and walk to the end of the counter, then turn right and look up.
Open the cupboard and put the egg on top of the plate.
Pick up the plate with the egg on it.
Turn to the right to face the fridge.
Put the plate with the egg on it on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Get a plate for the egg.

high_descs: Turn around, move forward, halfway across the room, turn left, go to the sink.
Pick up the egg on the counter.
Bring the egg to the cabinet left of the sink.
Put the egg on the plate in the cabinet.
Pick up the plate in the cabinet with egg on it.
Bring the plate right to the sink.
Put the plate with egg on the counter, right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with egg on it, on the counter, right of the sink.
